The Vampire can reroll missed close combat attacks in the first round of every combat.</description></rule></rules><costs><cost name="pts" typeId="ecfa-8486-4f6c-c249" value="25" /></costs></selection><selection id="xz4mq1" name="Red Fury" entryId="c1a6-882d-60f9-5b59::d846-d67c-02c6-6856" entryGroupId="c1a6-882d-60f9-5b59::84fd-049b-21b4-9075" number="1" type="upgrade" from="group" group="Magic and Traits::Blood dragon traits"><rules><rule id="4181-0833-b526-cdea" name="Red Fury" hidden="false"><description>The Vampire enters the melee as he has always done in centuries past with a savage and unstoppable bloodlust. He won't stop until all his enemies lie dead on the ground.
